secara patungan.

43
00:04:50,582 --> 00:04:52,126
RENCANA BISNIS
YOUR ARTWORK

44
00:04:52,209 --> 00:04:54,795
Kami butuh pakar
untuk memberi saran soal daftar karya,

45
00:04:55,629 --> 00:04:57,548
