94
00:09:43,333 --> 00:09:45,085
Tolong, Pak, aku mohon.

95
00:09:50,424 --> 00:09:51,258
Tidak!

96
00:09:51,842 --> 00:09:53,218
Jangan sentuh anak kami!

97
00:09:53,302 --> 00:09:54,678
Aku akan tanggung hukumannya!

98
00:09:54,761 --> 00:09:56,013
Lampiaskan saja padaku!

99
00:09:56,096 --> 00:09:58,849
Kubilang lampiaskan saja padaku!

100
00:09:58,932 --> 00:10:02,185
- Hentikan! Tidak!
- Lampiaskan padaku!

101
00:10:02,269 --> 00:10:03,312
<i>Dia tidak menangis.</i>

102
00:10:05,439 --> 00:10:06,690
<i>Dia menerimanya</i>

103
00:10:07,316 --> 00:10:08,775
